You can use roles and profiles to help you design and implement a better Puppet infrastructure.


True
False

Answer: True
Correct!

What gets assigned to nodes?

Roles
Classes
Modules
Profiles

Answer: Roles
Correct!

Roles are made up of:

exactly 1 profile
1 or more profiles
exactly 1 technology class
1 or more technology classes

Answer: 1 or more profiles
Correct!

Where do you declare class parameters?

Node
Role
Profile
Both Roles and Profiles

Answer: Profile
Correct!

